<p><a name="Comparison" id="Comparison"></a></p>
<h2><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Long_and_short_scales&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1" title="Edit section: Comparison">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Comparison</span></h2>
<p>For a more extensive table, see <b><a href="/wiki/Names_of_large_numbers" title="Names of large numbers">names of large numbers</a></b>.</p>
