<dd><span class="flagicon"><a href="/wiki/File:Flag_of_Bosnia_and_Herzegovina.svg" class="image" title="Flag of Bosnia and Herzegovina.svg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/bf/Flag_of_Bosnia_and_Herzegovina.svg/22px-Flag_of_Bosnia_and_Herzegovina.svg.png" width="22" height="11" border="0" class="thumbborder" /></a>&#160;</span><a href="/wiki/Bosnia_and_Herzegovina" title="Bosnia and Herzegovina">Bosnia and Herzegovina</a> (<a href="/wiki/Serbian_language" title="Serbian language">Serbian</a>: <a href="http://sr.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%BC%D0%B8%D0%BB%D0%B8%D1%98%D0%B0%D1%80%D0%B4%D0%B0" class="extiw" title="sr:милијарда">милијарда</a> <i>milijarda</i>, <a href="http://sr.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%91%D0%B8%D0%BB%D0%B8%D0%BE%D0%BD" class="extiw" title="sr:Билион">Билион</a> <i>bilion</i>; <a href="/wiki/Croatian_language" title="Croatian language">Croatian</a>: <i><a href="http://hr.wikipedia.org/wiki/milijarda" class="extiw" title="hr:milijarda">milijarda</a></i>, <i><a href="http://hr.wikipedia.org/wiki/bilijun" class="extiw" title="hr:bilijun">bilijun</a></i>)</dd>
