<li id="cite_note-Chuquet2-8"><b><a href="#cite_ref-Chuquet2_8-0" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFIdem">Idem. <a href="http://hexadecimal.florencetime.net/chuquet/triparty.htm" class="external text" title="http://hexadecimal.florencetime.net/chuquet/triparty.htm" rel="nofollow">"Nicolas Chuquet's chapter"</a>. Transcription by Michael Florencetime<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://hexadecimal.florencetime.net/chuquet/triparty.htm" class="external free" title="http://hexadecimal.florencetime.net/chuquet/triparty.htm" rel="nofollow">http://hexadecimal.florencetime.net/chuquet/triparty.htm</a></span><span class="reference-accessdate">. Retrieved on 2008-03-01</span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Nicolas+Chuquet%27s+chapter&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Idem&amp;rft.au=Idem&amp;rft.pub=Transcription+by+Michael+Florencetime&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fhexadecimal.florencetime.net%2Fchuquet%2Ftriparty.htm&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Long_and_short_scales"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span> <span class="languageicon" style="font-size:0.95em; font-weight:bold; color:#555;">(French)</span></li>
