<li id="cite_note-19"><b><a href="#cite_ref-19" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web"><a href="http://www.dieburger.com/Stories/Opinion/17.0.122900244.aspx" class="external text" title="http://www.dieburger.com/Stories/Opinion/17.0.122900244.aspx" rel="nofollow">"Biljoen gaan verwar"</a>. Die Burger<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://www.dieburger.com/Stories/Opinion/17.0.122900244.aspx" class="external free" title="http://www.dieburger.com/Stories/Opinion/17.0.122900244.aspx" rel="nofollow">http://www.dieburger.com/Stories/Opinion/17.0.122900244.aspx</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Biljoen+gaan+verwar&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.pub=Die+Burger&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.dieburger.com%2FStories%2FOpinion%2F17.0.122900244.aspx&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Long_and_short_scales"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-20"><b><a href="#cite_ref-20" title="">^</a></b> <cite style="font-style:normal" class="web" id="CITEREFKotz.C3.A9">Kotzé, E.F., Professor. <a href="http://152.111.1.251/argief/berigte/beeld/2008/02/20/B1/14/01milbiltril.html" class="external text" title="http://152.111.1.251/argief/berigte/beeld/2008/02/20/B1/14/01milbiltril.html" rel="nofollow">"Taalkommissie se reaksie op biljoen, triljoen"</a>. Die Taalkommissie van die Suid-Afrikaanse Akademie vir Wetenskap en Kuns<span class="printonly">. <a href="http://152.111.1.251/argief/berigte/beeld/2008/02/20/B1/14/01milbiltril.html" class="external free" title="http://152.111.1.251/argief/berigte/beeld/2008/02/20/B1/14/01milbiltril.html" rel="nofollow">http://152.111.1.251/argief/berigte/beeld/2008/02/20/B1/14/01milbiltril.html</a></span>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=bookitem&amp;rft.btitle=Taalkommissie+se+reaksie+op+biljoen%2C+triljoen&amp;rft.atitle=&amp;rft.aulast=Kotz%C3%A9&amp;rft.aufirst=E.F.%2C+Professor&amp;rft.au=Kotz%C3%A9%2C+E.F.%2C+Professor&amp;rft.pub=Die+Taalkommissie+van+die+Suid-Afrikaanse+Akademie+vir+Wetenskap+en+Kuns&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2F152.111.1.251%2Fargief%2Fberigte%2Fbeeld%2F2008%2F02%2F20%2FB1%2F14%2F01milbiltril.html&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Long_and_short_scales"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
